{"tid":1585742,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"打得好! 打得岩! 突破心理關口啦! 香港人向勝利方向前進","createTime":"2019-09-21T17:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T17:08:48.000Z","uid":258118,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d8046c6fa993d53bc2ae230b64f167173f1c45","tid":1585742,"uid":258118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"今日睇live 見大家 勇武既程度又進一步，對元朗牛屎黑社會藍屍 完全唔驚，更加 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以武制暴</span></span></strong>，保護同行既手足同記者急救員。 <br />\n<br />\n打既時候又記得打關節，又記得721，荃灣， 北角， 將軍澳既仇。<br />\n<br />\n大家進化了! 唔止暴力進化，係個<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">膽</span></span></strong></span></span></strong>進化! 心理上大家開始有 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">力量在於人民</span></span></strong> 既諗法，係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勝利既必要元素! </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然仲聽到少量人叫 &quot;唔好打&quot; 但係比起之前真係好左好多! Ukraine 革命既時候都係有呢d人，不過最終佢地即使唔打都唔會阻住勇武去打，因為佢地知道勇武係為左大家先會咁做。<br />\n<br />\n希望我地既阻膠都會變成 <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開遮</span></strong></span></span> 阻鏡頭既後排人士。 <br />\n<br />\n祝 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">武運昌隆</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}